@startuml Vertical Activity Flow
!theme plain
title Connectify AI — End‑to‑End Activity Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API" as API
database "DB" as DB
participant "AI" as AI
participant "WebSocket" as WS

== Register/Login ==
User -> FE: Register/Login
FE -> API: POST /register or /login
API -> DB: Create/Validate User
DB --> API: User record
API --> FE: JWT tokens
FE -> FE: Store tokens

== Upload Video ==
User -> FE: Upload video
FE -> API: POST /videos/upload
API -> DB: Create Video (status=uploading)
API -> AI: Trigger caption job
AI -> AI: Generate captions
AI -> DB: Save Caption rows
API -> DB: Update Video status=ready
API --> FE: Video + Captions

== Publish with Captions ==
User -> FE: Click "Publish with Captions"
FE -> API: PATCH /videos/{id}/ (caption settings)
API -> DB: Update Video
FE -> API: POST /videos/{id}/publish/
API -> DB: Create Post + PostMedia (copy captions)
API --> FE: 201 Created
FE -> FE: Navigate to Feed

== View Feed ==
User -> FE: Open Feed
FE -> API: GET /posts/
API -> DB: Fetch Posts + Media + Captions
DB --> API: Posts list
API --> FE: Serialized Posts
FE -> FE: Render PostCard(s) with VTT/overlay captions

== Like/Comment ==
User -> FE: Like post
FE -> API: POST /posts/{id}/like/
API -> DB: Create Like
API --> FE: 201

User -> FE: Comment
FE -> API: POST /posts/{id}/comments/
API -> AI: Analyze toxicity/sentiment
AI --> API: Scores
API -> DB: Create Comment
API --> FE: Serialized Comment

== Real‑time Chat ==
User -> FE: Open Messages
FE -> API: GET /chat/threads/
API -> DB: Threads
DB --> API: Threads list
API --> FE: Threads
User -> FE: Select thread
FE -> API: GET /chat/threads/{id}/messages/
API -> DB: Messages
DB --> API: Messages
API --> FE: Messages
FE -> WS: Connect ws://.../ws/chat/{threadId}/?token=jwt
WS -> FE: Authenticated
User -> FE: Send message
FE -> API: POST /chat/messages/
API -> DB: Create Message
API -> WS: Broadcast to group
WS -> FE: Push to participants

== Delete Post ==
User -> FE: Delete post (owner)
FE -> FE: Show confirmation
User -> FE: Confirm
FE -> API: DELETE /posts/{id}/
API -> DB: Delete Post (cascade)
API --> FE: 204
FE -> FE: Remove from UI, toast

== Translate Captions ==
User -> FE: Select language & translate
FE -> API: POST /videos/{id}/translate/
API -> AI: Translate captions
AI -> DB: Create translated Caption rows
API --> FE: Updated captions
FE -> FE: Re-render captions

@enduml
